 pressure because each Filipino athlete that qualifies for the Olympics really just wants to do the country proud,\\\" Alkhaldi told Rappler.\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my experience\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"your time\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 585}, {\"ngram\": \"good pressure\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"each Filipino athlete\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"Alkhaldi\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I think my advice is to really enjoy each moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my advice\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"each moment\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alkhaldi, the veteran national swimmer who represented the country in the 2012 London and 2016 Rio Olympics, said it's important for the athletes to also appreciate the hard work they have done.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999989695425, \"rank\": 1.030668454237495e-09, \"text\": \"2012 London\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alkhaldi\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"the veteran national swimmer\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 838},